column2: SELECT TOP #  S.ObjID, S.z,SN.sn_#,  &&&, L2.ew ,  &&&, L1.ew,  &&&,L3.ew FROM SpecPhoto AS S  JOIN SpecLine AS L1 ON S.SpecObjID = L1.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecObjAll AS SN ON S.SpecObjID = SN.SpecObjID  WHERE L1.LineId = #  and L2.LineId = #  and L3.LineID = # and (S.specclass=# or S.specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
